title: 工业mod安装后报错，求解决
txt_content:
IC2（非实验版）安装后报错
12:17:30 [严重] The mod IC2 is expecting signature de041f9f6187debbc77034a344134053277aa3b0 for source industrialcraft-2_1.118.401-lf-Fixed.jar, however there is no signature matching that description

12:17:36 [严重]Could not create inventory type ic2.core.block.generator.tileentity.TileEntityReactorChamberElectric Exception: java.lang.NullPointerException  
12:17:36 [严重]Could not determine default inventory size for type ic2.core.block.generator.tileentity.TileEntityReactorChamberElectric using size of 9        

...什么意思，要数字签名？无法创建目录？
这不重要，重要的是怎么解决......
还有IC2装的是http://www.mcbbs.net/thread-138244-1-1.html底下的修复版，服务器里IC2可以用
